      "content": "it's just that the rest you're talking about feels so heavy. like, i've checked all the boxes and the map is just... blank now. there aren't any more landmarks or sights that matter. it feels like i've reached the final destination and there aren't any more flights to catch or roads to drive. i don't really see the point in staying at the terminal waiting for a trip that isn't coming anymore.",
